---
// Theme Toggle - D√©monstration de variables CSS et th√®mes
---

<div class="theme-toggle-demo" x-data="{ isDark: false }">
  <div class="demo-header">
    <h3>D√©mo : Th√®me clair / sombre</h3>
    <button 
